    <item>
      <title>Blog: How to hone my craft?</title>
      <link>/blog/2020/08/27/how-to-hone-my-craft/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/blog/2020/08/27/how-to-hone-my-craft/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Author: Cal Newport&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accept my discomfort of learning anything I didn&amp;rsquo;t know very well&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be more patient and get more serious 😢&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hit the plateau first and reduce the unpredictable results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Increase my threshold of mental strain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate deliberate practice (not play 😢)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stretch my abilities systematically&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receive immediate feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

